Package org.esupportail.commons.exceptions

esup-commons exceptions.

See:
          Description

Exception Summary
ConfigException A class for configuration exceptions.
DownloadException A class for download exceptions.
EsupException An abstract class that should be inherited by all the user runtime exceptions.
ExceptionHandlingException A class thrown while handling exceptions.
GroupNotFoundException An exception thrown when failing to retrieve a group from a datasource.
NoRequestBoundException An exception thrown when no request is bound to thread.
ObjectNotFoundException A class to represent the exceptions thrown when expected objects do not exists (either retrieved from the database or configuration files).
PasswordException These exceptions are thrown when checking passwords.
RemoteEsupException An abstract class that should be inherited by all the remote services exceptions.
UserNotFoundException An exception thrown when failing to retrieve a user from a datasource.
WebFlowException A class for navigation exceptions.
